title: Daisy admires Gatsby's gold toilet set, and Gatsby laughs, overwhelmed by her presence and the realization of his long-held dream.

For half a minute there wasn’t a sound. Then from the living-room I

Daisy’s voice on a clear artificial note:

“I certainly am awfully glad to see you again.”
